<section class="recommendation publication		publication-article" id="publication" data-articleid="3364" data-module="PublicationView" data-priority="2">

	
	
	
	<header>

		
		<div class="publication-introduction publication-center">

							<h4 class="subtype-recommendation">Aanbeveling</h4>
			
			<div class="date-readingtime"><time data-field="date" datetime="2015-09-17" title="17-9-2015 5:45">
	2 uur geleden</time>
					
	
							
		<span class="reading-time">Leestijd
			4 minuten
		</span>

	
			</div>

			<p class="intro" data-field="intro">Vandaag verschijnt het nieuwe boek van Koen Haegens. Titel: <em>De grootste show op aarde. </em>Ondertitel: <em>De mythe van de markteconomie. </em>Bij dezen een warme aanbeveling.</p>

		</div>
		<h1 class="publication-title publication-center" data-field="title">Dit boek ontkracht een van de grootste mythes van onze tijd</h1><div class="publication-author-container"><div class="author"><p class="description">
      Correspondent&nbsp;Vooruitgang    </p><div class="image"><img width="190" class="lazyload" data-src="https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/ff-1433250313/media/380/556daa0953df37195798228.png" alt="Avatar Rutger Bregman"><noscript><img width="190" src="https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/ff-1433250313/media/380/556daa0953df37195798228.png" alt="Avatar Rutger Bregman"></noscript></div></div><div class="publication-author"><a rel="author" title="Meer van Rutger Bregman" href="/rutgerbregman" class="author-name">
  
  Rutger

  <span class="author-surname">Bregman</span></a><a href="#" id="followAuthor" title="Je volgt Rutger" class="follow-author-button-small delete-following-author following-author" data-author-id="15"><span></span></a></div></div></header>

	<div id="publicationMainImage" class="publication-main-image">

					
